INFO:

                * Don't forget to have a database (MySQL, PostgreSQL, msql...)
                 installed to use this API


POST-INSTALL:

		* Create the environment variable LTDL_LIBRARY_PATH:
		export LTDL_LIBRARY_PATH=/usr/lib

		* Copy the example files "odbcinst.ini" and "odbc.ini" in
		the "/etc" directory and create their corresponding links.
		# cp odbc*.ini /etc
		# ln -sf /etc/odbcinst.ini /usr/etc
		# ln -sf /etc/odbc.ini     /usr/etc
		

